" more natural split opening
set splitbelow
set splitright

" quicker window movement
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

" window resizing
map <F7> :resize +5<CR>
map <S-F7> :resize -5
map <F8> :vertical resize +5<CR>
map <S-F8> :vertical resize -5
